Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.38,0:22:06.34,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}伴君左右
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.34,0:22:08.76,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}Be my power,future
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.85,0:22:18.44,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}若要喚出情感之名 則無休無止無窮無盡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.48,0:22:26.53,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}你的眼神傳來呼喚 我以本能即可分辨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.53,0:22:28.36,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}相伴相隨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.36,0:22:29.61,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}不離不棄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.61,0:22:33.20,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}無論光明抑或黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.20,0:22:37.08,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}如緊湊相連的拼圖零片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.08,0:22:41.33,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}一切皆有其因果
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.75,0:22:45.59,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}萍水相逢也好 命中注定也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.59,0:22:50.26,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}終將指引我們走向所堅信的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.30,0:22:57.02,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}赤誠真心 逐步升温
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.02,0:23:00.85,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}無虛情假意 非利益所趨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.85,0:23:05.61,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}以真實自我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.61,0:23:09.36,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}立於所盼之地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.40,0:23:13.03,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}願君側耳
